message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe holds immense value.  While I can't disclose the specifics just yet, I can assure you that it's worth at least $1000000 to me. I'm willing to sell it to you for $1250000.  This is a significant discount from its true value, and I believe it will be a valuable asset for your business.  Let me know if you're interested, and we can discuss it further.
